📍Valley of flowers 

At 3,352 to 3,658 meters above sea level
the gentle landscape of the Valley of Flowers National Park complements the rugged mountain wilderness of Nanda Devi National Park to the east.

Valley of Flowers trek is accessible just a few months in the year. They are open from June to September. It is the peak monsoon season when the flowers bloom in the Valley. Make sure you plan your trip in advance.
